@ndavis17 RIGHT?!
I’ll take this date any day! 😍

@target Always! ❤️ The problem with our dates though is that I’m always spend so much on you. It’s like I give 100% and I only get 5% back.
@sam_robin26 this is hilarious! 👏👏👏
I met my husband at Target and we have been married for 25 years.
@vickyteaches Omg, Target love is the best love and this proves it. 😍
It’s funny because the first date my husband and I ever went on involved a shopping trip to Target. 11 years later we’re married and still love Target! ❤️
@rangerkinsmommy Love at first bullseye! 😍
@rangerkinsmommy  Maybe Target creates 💖 🤷🏻‍♀️
If only….
@lorizigg That's it, want to be our date?
@target sure 👏
Best date ever 🎯❤️
@_momochan3_ Us to our date "Ok, hear me out, a Target date, but add a little ✨spice✨"
@target my bf and I legit have target dates 😂
You had me at hot Cheetos and Oreos 😍
@liberatedsoul2 This is how we know we're soulmates. 😍
@liberatedsoul2 right? Me too
@target 🥰🥰
The most beautiful thing I’ve ever seen. 😍🤩
@paisley.ram We need a date here, asap!
Very cute, but how about a charcuterie board instead?! 😋
@decadentchaos that’s Tuesday’s menu 😋
@kelsij2 yes I was a kid in the 90s… however my palette is much more refined now! 😜
I didn’t meet my husband there, but I did work there when I met my husband? Does that count?
@the_world_according_to_pooh Yes. Yes it does.
😂👏🔥 this is awesome
@enriquezphillips So should we like date at a Target?

@target I think it has its potential for certain demographics. As a teen or young adult I would've think its awesome! Now if I saw two young lovebirds sitting by a red ball....I would be aww....how sweet. ❤️
Table for 2 adults and 4 kids tomorrow at noon. We'll all have the lunchable special. 😂
@jeniecescorner Right this way. 😉
What no Rose wine in a can?
@jensenchristy Only for you. 😘
Omg! The way I love this!
@candicedenise The way we do too!
Ew but why the lunchables?
@hanaheflick Excuse me, they're amazing that's why.
Nothing says romance like a date in a parking lot lol
@minnaloha Anything can be a date if you're at the right Target. ✨
I met my now husband at Target! And we did our engagement photos there!! 🎯
@missbeehavin88 thank you! 😊
@reb_larsen you're welcome 😊
“If you were an aisle, what aisle would you be and why?”
@the.gewinner I would be the electronic isle because people stop by to play but never buy the game
@the.gewinner  I would be makeup and face mask and cleanser section and clearance section!!!!
@the.gewinner  The wine isle🍷🍷😂
Ok so when can I come over?
@jviice_garbag Maybe after a second date. 💕
this better not be a joke
I do all my Target shopping on the app, I’ll be single forever😂
@brandilovesharlem Shipt n single lol 🙋🏻‍♀️
@brandilovesharlem 😂😂
@ginamvo aye you still got a chance with the right Shipt guy/gal. My target boxes get tossed in front of my door by the ups guy😂
Table for two please, you and me ♥️💃🏼
The perfect first date❤️
If a dude takes me on a date and there is a lunchable in sight.. I’m leaving..
@show_me_your_gassers I suppose this ad is geared toward college kids and not late 30’s lol
@janiskala  Same! Also, because I’m vegan!!!
@janiskala women love target so I assumed it was a male making the best of the situation 😂 🍕
Only if it’s in partnership with @jpokluda @kathy_davidson and @jenniesallen 👏🏼👏🏼 #outdated
The lunchables are much bigger than the UKs 😂😋
